Ahsoka Tano is known primarily for her appearances on Star Wars: The Clone Wars, Star Wars Rebels and, most recently, the hit Disney+ series The Mandalorian. She made her public debut in 2008 and went on to become a fan favourite despite not having physically appeared in any of the main saga films. Ahsoka did, however, have a brief voice cameo in 2019’s The Rise of Skywalker.
